          "reviewBody": "I had enrolled my 2.7 years old son for summer activities in Origin Play School. My son enjoyed the activities so much that he would get ready soon and say 'Origin school polam '. All the teachers were so friendly and he likes everyone and wil come home and talk about them to us. They made him mingle with everyone in the school and he had a great time there. Each and every teacher and the head mam of the school encouraged and took care of him so much that he learnt lot of new things. Every day, videos of the kids were sent and I was able to see what he did in the school that day. He made tremendous progress in speech, playing games, mingling with other kids and learning new things. All thanks to Origin Play school and the head mam for the care and love they gave and supported him to learn n grow well.",
